pin. Again, self-explanatory.</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/1fdpLNB.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>More tripwires</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/2sdrth3.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>Grenade pin secured to left door, grenade secured to right door. Pin is pulled when either door is opened.</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/9gCFq9H.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/alRIEEY.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/LV4G5gP.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>Pull pin from grenade and put it in a glass.

